@startuml 2A_Configure_Idol_Profile
title 2-A · Configure Idol Profile (UC-T03 to UC-T09)

start
|Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
:Log in to Tenant Admin;
:Open Idol Profile Management;

|System|
:Verify tenant status = ACTIVE;
:Load current idol profile, social links,\ngroup members and latest comeback data;

|Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
if (Admin action?) then (Update Profile)
  :Edit idol name, stage name, bio,\ndebut date and profile metadata;
  |System|
  :Validate required fields;
  :Save IdolProfile changes;
elseif (Admin action?) then (Upload Profile Images)
  :Choose avatar, cover or gallery image;
  |System|
  :Validate size, type and tenant storage;
  :Store image and link it to IdolProfile;
elseif (Admin action?) then (Manage Social Links)
  :Add, reorder, hide/show or remove social links;
  |System|
  :Validate URLs and save link order;
elseif (Admin action?) then (Create Idol Group)
  :Enter group name and description;
  |System|
  :Create IdolGroup for tenant;
elseif (Admin action?) then (Manage Group Members)
  :Add or edit member profile and role;
  |System|
  :Save group member list;
else (Announce Comeback)
  :Enter comeback title, date and announcement text;
  |System|
  :Save comeback announcement;
  :Notify eligible fans if notification enabled;
endif

|System|
:Update fansite cache/search data;
:Fans can view the updated idol profile;
stop
@enduml
